# docker-fluentd

* Fluend on Apline configured for shipping to Elastic

## Versions
- Alpine linux
- Fluentd ${FLUENTD_VERSION}
### Plugins
- fluent-plugin-elasticsearch ${FLUENTD_PLUGIN_ELASTIC}
- fluent-plugin-record-modifier ${FLUENTD_PLUGIN_RECORDMODIFIER}
- fluent-plugin-s3 ${FLUENTD_PLUGIN_S3}

## Usage

`docker run -p 9880:9880 -e ELASTIC_HOST=elastic-host -e ELASTIC_PORT=9200 --rm -it ${IMAGE_NAME}:${IMAGE_VERSION}`


